`8Keywords``   : Demonfire
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

`8Syntax:`` 

 * cast 'demonfire' <target>

 This is the summoning forth of the blazes that can only exist in the realm of
the demons.  Because of the nature of this spell, only those that follow the
path of the Dark Prophecy may use this spell.

